                <note rend="inline" type="source">325.1121 Bethune, Larry K./26: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-04-02T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 2, 1931—7 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 8:25 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>35. Department’s telegram 18, April 2, 2 p.m. Bethune’s detention incommunicado
                    was by order of the judge.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Culbertson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
